d679e02d-2bf0-4289-954b-d4699b1a8d03	2025-10-18 13:00:35.807699+00	2025-10-18 13:00:35.810007+00	\N	Communities Mobilise Against Eviction Threat	en-US	https://karibu.org.za/communities-mobilise-against-eviction-threat/		2025-09-04 19:46:19+00	f	0bddd603-1a24-418e-aa98-ba0b4e76d4b3	\N	<p>"In a climate of mounting evictions, austerity, and fragmented resistance, the Defend Public Spaces Campaign plans to meet the City of Joburg (CoJ) on 13 September 2025, at the Workers Museum (WM) in Newtown, to hand over a Petition. The..."</p>\n<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://karibu.org.za/communities-mobilise-against-eviction-threat/">Communities Mobilise Against Eviction Threat</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://karibu.org.za">Karibu - A Working Class News</a>.</p>\n
45829b11-d183-401f-8398-ca971711d1a2	2025-10-18 13:00:37.410714+00	2025-10-18 13:00:37.414293+00	\N	CONNECTING TO CRAFT	en-US	https://churchland.org.za/2023/12/05/connecting-to-craft/	\n<p>Exchange visits take place between various womens group to share skills on beadwork. Young crafters from groups like Xoshindlala share their skills with other crafters from groups like Thandanani.</p>\n<p>The ladies get practical training on how to weave scoobie wire to make earrings and bracelets. The trainees vary in age and are very keen to learn so that they can generate an income from the craft.</p>\n<p>With the influx of orders, young crafters are unable to juggle their time between chores and other responsibilities. Sometimes exchange visits even become a challenge.</p>\n<p>Crafters do exchange visits to train each other. Young crafters learn more things because they have access to the internet. YouTube helps them to learn and to stay current. </p>\n\n  \n    <div class="row large-columns-4 medium-columns-3 small-columns-2" >\n  <div class="gallery-col col" >\n          <div class="col-inner">\n            <a class="image-lightbox lightbox-gallery" href="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-1.jpg" title="">            <div class="box has-hover gallery-box box-overlay dark">\n              <div class="box-image" >\n                <img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" width="960" height="1280" src="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-1.jpg" class="attachment-original size-original" alt="" ids="4935,4936,4937,4938" lightbox_image_size="original" image_size="original" srcset="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-1.jpg 960w, https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-1-225x300.jpg 225w, https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-1-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" />                                  <div class="overlay fill"\n                      style="background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.15)">\n                  </div>\n                                                              </div>\n              <div class="box-text text-left" >\n                 <p></p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            </a>          </div>\n         </div><div class="gallery-col col" >\n          <div class="col-inner">\n            <a class="image-lightbox lightbox-gallery" href="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-2.jpg" title="">            <div class="box has-hover gallery-box box-overlay dark">\n              <div class="box-image" >\n                <img decoding="async" width="960" height="1280" src="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-2.jpg" class="attachment-original size-original" alt="" ids="4935,4936,4937,4938" lightbox_image_size="original" image_size="original" srcset="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-2.jpg 960w, https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-2-225x300.jpg 225w, https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-2-768x1024.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px" />                                  <div class="overlay fill"\n                      style="background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.15)">\n                  </div>\n                                                              </div>\n              <div class="box-text text-left" >\n                 <p></p>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n            </a>          </div>\n         </div><div class="gallery-col col" >\n          <div class="col-inner">\n            <a class="image-lightbox lightbox-gallery" href="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Exchange-3.jpg" title="">            <div class="box has-hover gallery-box box-overlay dark">\n              <div class="box-image" >\n                <img decoding="async" width="960" height="1280" src="https://churchland.org.za/wp-content/