eb15bd65-52fb-45af-a110-71fb56ed23e4	2025-10-18 13:01:10.652079+00	2025-10-18 13:01:10.654385+00	\N	The Movement of the Poor Turns Twenty on Saturday	en-ZA	https://abahlali.org/node/18517/		2025-10-02 09:09:28+00	f	1198c9d0-3af9-4671-bb0e-4a926aa34904	\N	2 October 2025 Abahlali baseMjondolo The Movement of the Poor Turns Twenty on Saturday Our movement was formed on 4 October 2005 by 32 elected representatives from 12 settlements. Today we have more than 180 000 members organised into more than 100 branches across five provinces. In twenty years of struggle we have suffered and<a href="https://abahlali.org/node/18517/">Continue reading <span class="sr-only">"The Movement of the Poor Turns Twenty on Saturday"</span></a>
