e-healthcare-in-sa-a-deep-dive-into-profits-power-inequality-kaya-959/">Who Really Owns Private Healthcare in SA? A Deep Dive into Profits, Power &#038; Inequality | KAYA 959</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.opensecrets.org.za">Open Secrets</a>.</p>\n	2025-10-01 10:00:11+00	f	0744ad9c-d1c8-45d1-863d-0ccd1723ada7	\N	<p>South Africas two-tier health system is under the microscope again  and in the latest instalment of Who Owns South Africa, Open Secrets peels back the curtain on private medical aids and hospital groups. Phemelo Motene speaks to Open Secrets Head of Investigations, Michael Marchant, about the money, the monopolies, and the future of our health system. </p>\n<p>The post <a href="https://www.opensecrets.org.za/who-really-owns-private-healthcare-in-sa-a-deep-dive-into-profits-power-inequality-kaya-959/">Who Really Owns Private Healthcare in SA? A Deep Dive into Profits, Power &#038; Inequality | KAYA 959</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.opensecrets.org.za">Open Secrets</a>.</p>\n
