 2025\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class="wpb_raw_code wpb_raw_html wpb_content_element" >\n\t\t<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n\t\t\t<iframe loading="lazy" src="https://omny.fm/shows/power-podcasts/creative-corner-who-owns-south-africa-the-system-money-power-and-politics/embed?style=Cover" width="100%" height="180" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write" frameborder="0" title="CREATIVE CORNER: Who Owns South Africa: The System- Money, Power and Politics"></iframe>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div class="wpb_text_column wpb_content_element " >\n\t\t<div class="wpb_wrapper">\n\t\t\t<p>Michael Marchant, Head of Investigations at Open Secrets, interviewed on POWER 98.7 about the Who Owns South Africa? (WOSA) series. Its first profile, The System: Money, Power and Politics, explores how concentrated wealth and corporate dominance influence policy, deepen inequality, and hinder social progress. By highlighting the gap between the elite and millions dependent on social grants, the series seeks to promote transparency, empower citizens, and hold powerful actors accountable.</p>\n\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n<div class='root-data-givewp-embed' data-form-locale='en_GB' data-form-url='https://www.opensecrets.org.za/?post_type=give_forms&#038;p=12186' data-form-view-url='https://www.opensecrets.org.za/?givewp-route=donation-form-view&form-id=12186' data-src='https://www.opensecrets.org.za/?givewp-route=donation-form-view&form-id=12186' data-givewp-embed-id='give-form-shortcode-10' data-form-format='' data-open-form-button='Donate now' style='--givewp-primary-color: #ffec00; --givewp-secondary-color: #000000;'></div></div></div></div><div class="wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4"><div class="vc_column-inner vc_custom_1753870869912"><div class="wpb_wrapper">\n<div class="vc_grid-container-wrapper vc_clearfix vc_grid-animation-fadeIn">\n\t<div class="vc_grid-container vc_clearfix wpb_content_element vc_basic_grid vc_custom_1754397427899" data-initial-loading-animation="fadeIn" data-